****************************************************Docker file creation and app deployment (python app deployment using ubuntu)****************************************

Step 1. vi Dockerfile #add docker file related data
Step 2: vi app.py #add code
Step 3: vi requirements.txt #add the reuqirments
Step 4: docker build -t img1 . #is used in Docker to create a Docker image from a Dockerfile.
Step 5: docker run -dt img1 #Creates and starts a new container from an image without login. if you want to login to container add docker run -it img1
Step 6: docker run -dt -p 5000:5000 img1 #runs a container using Docker and exposes a port so you can access the app from your machine.

